### GET request ratings for a podcast
# @name Get Ratings for a Podcast
# @query podcastName The name of the podcast to retrieve ratings for
# @response 200 OK Returns the ratings for the specified podcast
GET {{baseUrl}}/ratings?podcastName={{podcastName}}

###

### Create a new rating for a podcast
# @name Create Rating for a Podcast
# @body podcastName The name of the podcast to rate
POST {{baseUrl}}/ratings
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "podcastName": "{{podcastName}}",
    "rating": {{rating}}
}
